 #444; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-seri=
f; margin: 0 0 1em;">Publicado em <a style=3D"text-decoration: underline; c=
olor: #2585B2;"  href=3D"http://www.freemasons-freemasonry.com/journey1.htm=
l">http://www.freemasons-freemasonry.com/journey1.html</a></p>=0A<div style=
